Hardening report is missing required sections:
  - ## Pre-Clean Results
  - ## Instrumentation Summary
  - ## Edge Case Tests Generated
  - ## Red Team Findings
  - ## Post-Clean Results
  - ## WYSIATI Coverage Sweep
  - ## Evidence Ledger
  - ## Verdict

All hardening reports must include these sections per the Phase 4.5 spec.
See docs/specs/2026-03-26-reliability-hardening-phase-design.md for the required format.
